{"ha0c2bb4dg293bg4b01gadadg3e9cd5754219": ["After all you did, I pegged you as a person of good standing. Guess I was wrong.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "3af4b4d1-993f-c91c-39d2-8683aa476b1c"], "hdbb8176cgda48g4254g898bg2ae4b399b1bd": ["Good luck with your new friends. They'll stab you in your sleep, but at least you'll be remembered as a real bastard.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "75276fe5-b3e5-bd8b-72c0-832f72952295"], "hdcaaf8bbg1cd0g4ad8gb8ccgfef53308b9e5": ["Oh, go enjoy your party.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "72d847e2-d71a-42a8-4b28-f529f6570510"], "h19f569a4gb12cg470bgb026g20cdc805a3ce": ["Hmm.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "07ec5e75-b1d7-6d1e-5f9d-61e4128bcb7b"], "h8e2b310agd3e6g42f2g9a76g467c5399a4c6": ["What are you doing?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "f56ec3af-2639-514d-af90-1622caf0f19d"], "h9d330649ge485g47a1g91b5gfa718757feec": ["Working.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "171d8698-0ad8-d42d-f121-9340e814b8ba"], "h8178a3e0g5490g413ag9d41ga868b0065540": ["<i>Hand him a drink.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "588f7dd2-9eb4-9cee-cc84-169e48517e2a"], "ha21180a4gf62ag41adg8b46gd631b21403e5": ["You can take that back. It's in the way.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "62003ff9-beaf-a529-ff4f-746c841f6e71"], "h115182a1gded4g4b4egb81cg5320fe7c93c6": ["<i>Lean in close to inspect what he is making.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "1a0d975e-6733-8244-e1de-175de6265826"], "h12b796a8g7ef7g4a6eg91cag1d7ea2fbd6ab": ["*A choking sulphur stench wafts from the twigs Barcus is cautiously assembling - explosive arrows.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "2f12b31f-3baf-672d-70f3-11bf67d7a36e"], "h6241224agfb39g4d64ga49dgd621d75b5525": ["Do you mind? I am <i>trying </i>to work.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "2ac2ef23-bcb0-ca7c-bb1f-ee030ee6da2c"], "hd6453672g2e52g4c46g8a19gc0c211eee995": ["Interesting. You're quite the craftsman.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "6cc1ed66-8c09-726b-1389-218a5bc9bd0f"], "h28e120ebgae2eg4d36gb233g03d42d3a53c9": ["Yes, thank you. Now please...?", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "2b8f4e1d-dabd-ba9e-e20b-1fda6a0430df"], "h7fb3aec3gd140g4b23g8b0dgb84e4068d3bd": ["That's the thing - you're working when you should be celebrating.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "6a1f34ee-c232-d173-e77c-1f53b5757fa0"], "he07411e2gf0d8g426dgbe80g76df792eae49": ["Celebrate? I appreciate that you're proud of your victory, but it's just that. Yours.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "113f9518-0188-229b-fc58-d03083dd848e"], "hff7ac094ge0fcg4604g9c34g5167c94e4019": ["Wulbren is still missing, and there are gnomes trapped in Moonrise Towers.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "aaba7509-aa18-11e9-b3f2-a8825392d1e2"], "h6b0480e7g6261g435dgb433g5d9af10096cf": ["Me drinking beer won't save them.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "f7973f30-869b-9399-6980-ef149f48203a"], "h22ac3aacg8ef0g4debg9c2egc17074129aa0": ["No, but a break might help your concentration.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "b82e19e7-d624-c59f-3220-91eb89ce73db"], "h6dadee81g6c5ag4ed4gafabg58d0fb5391d9": ["You leaving would help my concentration.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "fdfa4464-f0f4-9d48-1aa8-c84b2a434c25"], "h0ebf2609g49cbg4587g9a5age5e38289f3d6": ["But if you insist...", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "d535f665-44ce-98dc-e3a7-9613e814c576"], "ha46672d2g82c3g4c1ag9c5egf3553626add7": ["There. Celebration.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "fde4f511-6251-8cc5-c482-2f31bc213af3"], "h054e2b7eg442dg487ag9b78gad34f11587b3": ["I understand. I'm sorry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "ee3ec880-37c7-2f0f-4275-d37df6f98cd0"], "h4661f5f4gfd1cg4252ga3cdg32a3540f9e0b": ["Do you? ...You can't solve all the world's problems. I don't expect you to.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "f40eb435-6845-b498-6cfa-98c572672a31"], "h74076085gd873g46a3ga592g68aad6617c68": ["But... here. Take one of my old stock. I'm sure you'll find a good use for it.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "904a35aa-0ad7-4723-1269-906f1b418b5b"], "h97d58262g916ag42a1gae21g081d9e8702d8": ["Fair enough. So what are you making?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "8c52aac9-00a3-a60e-90f4-dc024d64749e"], "h133ad545g4aecg4745g873fg3757b5850f1a": ["Explosive arrows. Here, take one of my old stock and begone.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "2a1cdd31-5f30-58ee-6227-a4be65be21de"], "ha8829fbcg8b5ag46d4g869bgf56d25ad4cb5": ["And arrows will?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "079304a2-7dd2-34ea-5d60-7894cd1f7fed"], "h9a36a576g8ceag4a03g8125gce3554385fe9": ["Your friends are as good as dead. You might as well relax.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "12dd559e-ff21-b92d-a943-b1023b226180"], "h4f2b1d53gb0e0g4b06g9623g3aa415173913": ["Hmph. I thought you'd understand. Guess not.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "4ca22339-5772-e336-e0d1-7735dfb4526b"], "hb1a65fa8gf9e2g4185g88e6g8f0548ac2b20": ["Suit yourself, but you should join us when you're done.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "57c01b71-15a8-cb6c-a157-d665e0e00a1e"], "h854daf43g9cccg43e6gb061g0a96b7b77e07": ["I appreciate that you're proud of your victory, but it's just that. Yours.", "6e45a00b-bad2-40bb-9403-147b9e92d976", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "7279f712-f221-37ef-5583-580d38c8bc2a"], "h244e8534g8695g496bg8500gb196b7dd95b3": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "b14468fe-c664-7907-9a8f-f1ba9f135df5"], "h0c518e24gef5eg47f9g9e2egbf4ae840f271": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_UnfortunateGnome.html", "e343bafe-45b1-01c0-d25e-19b443b803a6"]}